                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "text",
                    "source": "Challenge existing processes Inspire a shared vision",
                    "target": "挑战现有流程，激发共同愿景"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "text",
                    "source": "higher level of independence, self-reliance, self-trust, and the capacity to exercise initiative",
                    "target": "更高的独立性、自力更生、自我信任以及发挥主动性的能力"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "text",
                    "source": "I lived at number twenty-three Blenheim Road for five years, blissfully happy and utterly wretched",
                    "target": "我在布伦海姆路二十三号住了五年，既幸福得无比欣喜又痛苦得彻底"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "text",
                    "source": "Life is not a paragraph, and death is no parenthesis",
                    "target": "人生不是一段文字，死亡也不是括号"
